Municipal Accountant to immediately return the excess amount of P19,800.00 to the source agency; 

Municipal Health Office in coordination with the MHRMO to prepare the necessary documents to reimburse the Disbursing Officer for the deficit in the cash advance totaling P13,500.00; 

